    "Furthermore, we will highlight the applications of AI in genome analysis and personalized medicine (see Fig. 3).",
    "AI is revolutionizing the way healthcare professionals identify, manage, and control diseases.",
    "AI algorithms can rapidly analyze large datasets of clinical symptoms and laboratory test results to detect diseases at early stages.",
